## Asset images are not versioned in git — they live on local disk and are
## either (a) regenerated by the sprite packer (atlas PNGs) or (b) distributed
## out-of-band. The text sidecar files (*.spritemeta, *.animationmeta) stay
## tracked because they're what tells the game where each sprite lives.
## Fresh clones will have no asset images — copy them in manually.
assets/**/*.png

